<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{{AGENT_NAME}} — plan-billed agent</title>
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
      body {
        font: 16px/1.55 ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        max-width: 46rem; margin: 3rem auto; padding: 0 1.25rem;
      }
      h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
      .tag {
        display: inline-block; font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 999px; background: #e8f0fe; color: #1a56db;
      }
      table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 1rem 0; }
      th, td { text-align: left; padding: 0.45rem 0.6rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; vertical-align: top; }
      th { width: 11rem; color: #555; font-weight: 600; }
      code { background: rgba(127,127,127,0.14); padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem; border-radius: 4px; }
      .muted { color: #777; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>{{AGENT_NAME}} <span class="tag">runs on your plan · no API key</span></h1>
    <p>{{ONE_LINE_PURPOSE}}</p>

    <table>
      <tr><th>What it does</th><td>{{PURPOSE}}</td></tr>
      <tr><th>Success looks like</th><td>{{SUCCESS_CRITERIA}}</td></tr>
      <tr><th>Agent file</th><td><code>.claude/agents/{{AGENT_NAME}}.md</code></td></tr>
      <tr><th>Tools</th><td><code>{{ALLOWLIST}}</code></td></tr>
      <tr><th>Model</th><td>{{MODEL}}</td></tr>
      <tr><th>Trigger</th><td>{{on-demand | Routine cadence | cron | GitHub event}}</td></tr>
      <tr><th>Run it</th><td>See <code>LAUNCH.md</code></td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Roadmap</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>v1:</strong> {{NEXT_STEP}}</li>
      <li><strong>v2:</strong> {{LATER_STEP}}</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="muted">
      Plan-billed sibling of anthropics/launch-your-agent. Subagent + headless
      <code>claude -p</code> + optional Routine/cron — all on your Claude
      subscription.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
